node.text:
Well, if not you are missing out! They have this seamless special keratin bonding technology that can give you almost any style you want! They are really small so you can barely feel them and they last 4-6 months! They are also almost undetectable y’all and the extensions are ethically sourced so it's a win-win! They are just overall BOMB!🔥

Stylist @nancileehair

Salon @kimvosalon

#howiwearmygl #ad

node.text: Check out my quick (and Mommy Approved) hair wash routine. All you need is a few minutes of selfcare with the Imbue 4-step regimen to get gorgeous curls, it's perfect for those busy days balancing work and mom duties! They have some of the best products that are made to be gentle on your hair and help bring it back to health and make it easy to do any style after this 4 step regimen. If you haven’t tried @imbuecurlsusa you’re missing out! #ad #Imbue, #ImbueCurls #IMBUEtiful, #JoinTheCurlMovement

node.text:
It’s my BIRRFFFFFDDDDAAAYYYY!!!🥳 I can’t believe I turned 30 again! 😆 Thank you Lord for another year & thank you all for your constant love & support. 🥺 My bday was actually July 31 but you know us Leo’s celebrate the whole season! Where are my Lions🦁?!!! 
Love y’all!💕
#leoseason
